            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Matronis <lb n="2"/>Alhiahen<lb break="no" n="3"/>abus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Verani<lb break="no" n="5"/>us Super pr<lb break="no" n="6"/>o se et su<lb break="no" n="7"/>is <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in sek. Verwendung als Weihwasserbecken. Iul. eventuell auch als praenomen zu verstehen.</p>
            </div>
